For information about marijuana (aka hemp) history, visit the Hemp History section. For information about medical marijuana or recent legislative efforts visit the recent <A HREF="/News/index.tpl">News</A> or the <A HREF="/Reference/Medicine/index.tpl">Medical</A> section.<P>

We also encourage you to visit the <A HREF="../Reference/links/index.tpl">Links</A> section, where there's even more material.<P>

